00:38:09.269 --> 00:38:14.220
of traditional systems, usually state run
systems. And you sort of have the paradox

00:38:14.220 --> 00:38:18.990
in some places where there will be an elite
public university which is free, which sounds

00:38:18.990 --> 00:38:22.880
very egalitarian. But it turns out that to
