sector and in a place like India, there have

00:40:36.120 --> 00:40:39.790
been huge strides in India. I mean you know,
certainly in the broader economy the idea

00:40:39.790 --> 00:40:44.109
of central planning is now out of vogue, and
that's why India has grown in my view. I think

00:40:44.109 --> 00:40:49.250
you need to bring that same sort of mentality
to the higher education system.

